descriptionHtml:
[center][size=5]
Hello! this time my Character Preset for RaceMenu
is a HighElf, her name is Mavfrei [/size][size=5][size=5]feel free to play with her
as your character[/size].


[size=5]Sorry cuz i cant make my presets to become a follower,
[/size][/size][size=5][size=5] i tried my best to make one but i failed :D[/size][/size][/center]

[size=6]Requirements:[/size]

[size=3][url=http://skse.silverlock.org/]SKSE[/url][/size]
[size=3][url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/29624/?]Racemenu
[/url][url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/2666/?]CBBE[/url][/size]
[size=3][url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/58221/?]KS Hairdo's[/url][/size]
[size=3][url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/30411/?]Brows[/url][/size][url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/59192]
[/url][size=3][url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/13722]The Eyes Of Beauty
[/url][url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/31665/?]Better Makeup
[/url][url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/51602/?]Fair Skin Complexion*[/url][/size]

[size=6]Recommended:[/size]

[size=3][url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/35303/?]Female Facial Animation
[/url][url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/54509]Familiar Faces[/url][/size]  (if you want to try them as your follower, cuz idont have the skills to make one)

[size=6]Installation:[/size]

[size=3]Step-1. Download my mod and place it at Data/SKSE/plugins/CharGen/Presets

[size=3]Step-[/size]2. Start Skyrim using SKSE loader

[size=3]Step-[/size]3. Load any working save file or start a newgame

[size=3]Step-[/size]4. Open the console " ~ "

[size=3]Step-[/size]5. Type "showracemenu"

[size=3]Step-[/size]6. Select the HighElf Race. (if you dont want to be a HighElf choose other Race, then use "Sculpt" inside RaceMenu
            then click "Import Head" choose "HighElf Mavfrei Head" do this after "Step-7 and Step-8".)

[size=3]Step-[/size]7. Look for "Preset" inside RaceMenu

[size=3]Step-[/size]8. Press F9, then click "HighElf Mavfrei"

[size=3]Step-[/size]9. Play! have fun... :D
[/size][center][size=4]

[size=5]Feel free to use All My Presets
in your Mods or any mods[/size]
(it would be nice to see my presets walking around in skyrim world as a real follower or a replacer)


My Other Presets
[/size][size=3][url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/82645]DarkElf Leirifa Preset

[/url][/size]
[/center][size=4][center]Credits
to All :D[/center][/size]
